title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.7 - Directions of attendant
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.7 - Directions of attendant

State Regulations

All permit holders are required to obey the directions
of the OGS parking lot attendant (i.e., to utilize a parking space as directed, etc.). Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
296-1.7

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
